# Stage 7: Backend lowering

Builder handoff, target validation and artifact production.

## Contract

- Input: compiled modules, borrow facts, builder metadata and selected backend
- Output: backend artifacts and explicit output-file records
- Decides: target-specific code generation, backend feature validation, project artifact assembly
- Must not decide: frontend semantics, HIR shape, source syntax
- Invariant: backend lowerers consume validated HIR and companion metadata without rediscovering frontend facts

## Main paths

- `src/backends/js/`
- `src/backends/wasm/`
- `src/backends/backend_feature_validation.rs`
- `src/projects/html_project/`

